description:
In episode 752, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Brandie Posey to discuss election results coming in, Trump claiming victory, Oregon decriminalizing drugs, and more good results!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Presidential Election Results
  2. As America Awaits a Winner, Trump Falsely Claims He Prevailed
  3. U.S. Senate Election Results
  4. Oregon first state to legalize hallucinogenic 'magic' mushrooms
  5. Oregon decriminalizes possession of street drugs, becoming first in nation
  6. George Gascón holds lead in L.A. County district attorney race
  7. WELP: Guess How Many People Kanye Got to Vote for ‘President Kanye’
  8. WATCH: Resonate by Tomos
